InvoiceOcean,is,an,online,invoicing,service,designed,to,have,a,simple,and,intuitive,interface,It,can,send,invoices,in,many,languages,and,in,all,world,currencies,The,user,s,data,is,securely,stored,in,the,cloud,and,can,be,accessed,anywhere,The,InvoiceOcean,API,allows,users,to,easily,integrate,the,service,s,functions,and,stored,data,into,their,own,applications